title: S. Gnanathiraviam
summary: Samiyadiyan Gnanathiraviam is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, lower house of the Parliament of India from Tirunelveli, Tamil Nadu in the 2019 Indian general election as member of the Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam.
content:
Samiyadiyan Gnanathiraviam is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, lower house of the Parliament of India from Tirunelveli, Tamil Nadu in the 2019 Indian general election as member of the Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam.
